OL,6,FA planned relaxation of rules around
OL,7,Fairline passengers carrying liquids in
OL,8,Fhand luggage has been delayed by a
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FThe Government announced it has
OL,12,Fgranted extensions to several large UK
OL,13,Fairports, including Gatwick, unable to
OL,14,Fmeet its June 1 deadline to fully
OL,15,Finstall new scanning technology.
