OL,3,CEasing of airport security liquid
OL,4,Crules delayed by a year
OL,6,FThe new scanners produce more detailed
OL,7,Fimages, meaning passengers can be
OL,8,Fallowed to pass through airport
OL,9,Fsecurity with containers holding up to
OL,10,Ftwo litres of liquid in their hand
OL,11,Fluggage.
OL,13,FAt airports which have not put them in
OL,14,Fplace, the limit remains 100ml and
OL,15,Fcontainers must be put in clear
OL,16,Fplastic bags.
OL,18,FThe new scanners also end the need for
OL,19,Flaptops and tablets to be removed from
OL,20,Fhand luggage.
