OL,3,CEasing of airport security liquid
OL,4,Crules delayed by a year
OL,6,FA deadline of December 2022 for most
OL,7,Fmajor airports to deploy new scanners
OL,8,Fwas initially set in August 2019 by
OL,9,Fthen-prime minister Boris Johnson.
OL,11,FAfter the aviation industry suffered
OL,12,Fhuge disruption due to coronavirus
OL,13,Ftravel restrictions, in December 2022,
OL,14,FTransport Secretary Mark Harper set a
OL,15,Fnew date of June 1 2024.
OL,17,FHe said at the time this would reduce
OL,18,Fqueuing times.
