OL,3,CEasing of airport security liquid
OL,4,Crules delayed by a year
OL,6,FMany airports are struggling to
OL,7,Finstall the scanners ahead of the busy
OL,8,Fsummer holiday period, largely due to
OL,9,Fsupply chain delays and construction
OL,10,Fdifficulties caused by the weight of
OL,11,Fthe machines.
OL,13,FMinisters have issued extensions of up
OL,14,Fto 12 months to several airports on a
OL,15,Fcase by case basis, which is expected
OL,16,Fto be enough time for them all to
OL,17,Fcomplete the work.
OL,19,FThe Government is also exploring how
OL,20,Ffinancial penalties could be imposed
OL,21,Ffor further non-compliance.
