OL,4,Crules delayed by a year
OL,6,FThe Department for Transport refused
OL,7,Fto provide a breakdown of the
OL,8,Fsituation for each airport, citing
OL,9,Fsecurity concerns.It said by the start
OL,10,Fof June about half of passengers
OL,11,Fflying from UK airports will be
OL,12,Fprocessed by the new scanners.
OL,14,FBut passengers are advised to prepare
OL,15,Fto follow the existing rules, and
OL,16,Fcheck with their airport for any
OL,17,Fchanges.
