OL,6,FMr Harper said, "These cutting-edge
OL,7,Fscanners will make air travel safer
OL,8,Fand easier for passengers by
OL,9,Fstrengthening security even further."
OL,11,F"The UK is leading the world with its
OL,12,Frollout of this technology, but it's
OL,13,Fimportant we give those airports yet
OL,14,Fto meet the deadline a second chance
OL,15,Fto get the job done."
OL,17,F"Until they do, passengers should
OL,18,Fcontinue to check before travelling."
