OL,3,CEasing of airport security liquid
OL,4,Crules delayed by a year
OL,6,FHeathrow has previously said it
OL,7,Fexpects to have new scanners in all
OL,8,Fsecurity lanes this summer, while
OL,9,FGatwick expects to complete the
OL,10,Fprogramme by the end of March next
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FManchester Airports Group, which runs
OL,14,FManchester, East Midlands and Stansted
OL,15,Fairports, said its scanners will be
OL,16,Ffully rolled out in 2025.
OL,18,FLondon City become the UK's first
OL,19,Fmajor airport to begin using the new
OL,20,Fscanners for all passengers in April
OL,21,Flast year.
