OL,6,FKaren Dee, chief executive of trade
OL,7,Fbody the Airport Operators
OL,8,FAssociation, said, "Airports are
OL,9,Fmaking excellent progress in
OL,10,Fdelivering these multi-million-pound
OL,11,Finvestment programmes, which will
OL,12,Fensure the UK remains at the forefront
OL,13,Fof aviation security in the years
OL,14,Fahead."
OL,16,F"As with any programme of this
OL,17,Fcomplexity, there are significant
OL,18,Fchallenges, and we are happy the
OL,19,FGovernment has recognised these and
OL,20,Fagreed to extend timeframes for
OL,21,Fdelivery where necessary."
