OL,6,FNaomi Leach, deputy editor of Which?
OL,7,FTravel, said, "Passengers should have
OL,8,Fbeen looking forward to a more
OL,9,Fefficient security process at the UK's
OL,10,Fbiggest airports this summer. Instead,
OL,11,Fwith different rules and processes now
OL,12,Flikely to apply at different airports,
OL,13,Fthe ensuing confusion could lead to
OL,14,Ffurther delays."
